    <button id="show2" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" onclick="show2()">Glass</button>

    <div style="display:none" id="content2">
        <h4>Top tips on how to reuse glass:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Reuse glass drink bottles as a liqued soap dispenser.</li>
            <li>Decorate bottles by painting them and use it as decor around the house.</li>
            <li>Use glass jars as additional storage, example keeping sweets in.</li>
        </ul>

        <button id="less2" class="btn btn-danger btn-block" onclick="less2()">Less</button>
    </div>

